    </sentence>
    <sentence id="DDI-DrugBank.d450.s14" text="Furthermore, caution should be exercised when combining digoxin with any drug that may cause a significant deterioration in renal function, since a decline in glomerular filtration or tubular secretion may impair the excretion of digoxin.">
